{"builtWith":"0.15.15","comments":[{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":"                                          // hydrogen // gpu // kernel // text"},{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":" | Text Rendering Kernels — SDF Glyph Rendering for Ghostty-class Terminals"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Purpose"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | High-performance text rendering requires GPU acceleration. SDF (Signed"},{"LineComment":" | Distance Field) rendering enables:"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - Resolution-independent glyphs (infinite zoom without pixelation)"},{"LineComment":" | - Smooth anti-aliasing at any scale"},{"LineComment":" | - GPU-efficient text effects (outlines, shadows, glow)"},{"LineComment":" | - Subpixel positioning for crisp text"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## SDF Rendering Pipeline"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ```"},{"LineComment":" | Font -> SDF Atlas Generation -> Glyph Cache"},{"LineComment":" |                                    |"},{"LineComment":" | Text String -> Layout -> Glyph Instances -> SDF Render Kernel"},{"LineComment":" |                                                |"},{"LineComment":" |                                          Composited Output"},{"LineComment":" | ```"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Ghostty Architecture Reference"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Ghostty achieves 120fps terminal rendering via:"},{"LineComment":" | - Pre-rasterized SDF atlas (one-time cost per font)"},{"LineComment":" | - Instanced rendering (one draw call for entire screen)"},{"LineComment":" | - Subpixel anti-aliasing (ClearType-style LCD rendering)"},{"LineComment":" | - Compute shader for text layout"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## At Billion-Agent Scale"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Text kernels are deterministic:"},{"LineComment":" | - Same font + text + size = same output (always)"},{"LineComment":" | - Glyph atlases are content-addressed (UUID5 from font data)"},{"LineComment":" | - Text layout is pure function of input string + font metrics"},{"LineComment":" | - Multiple agents can share atlas cache efficiently"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Module Structure"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | This module re-exports from submodules:"},{"LineComment":" | - `Text.Types` — Core ADTs and type aliases"},{"LineComment":" | - `Text.Vector` — GPU vector types (Vec2, Vec3, Vec4)"},{"LineComment":" | - `Text.Math` — Interpolation, SDF, color packing"},{"LineComment":" | - `Text.Dispatch` — Workgroup/dispatch calculations"},{"LineComment":" | - `Text.Composition` — Kernel sequencing and cost estimation"},{"LineComment":" | - `Text.Predicates` — Testing conditions on kernels/effects"},{"LineComment":" | - `Text.Presets` — Ready-to-use pipelines"}],"decls":[],"exports":[],"foreign":[],"imports":[{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[295,4],"start":[250,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","GPU","Kernel","Text","Composition"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[248,4],"start":[242,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","GPU","Kernel","Text","Dispatch"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[240,4],"start":[214,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","GPU","Kernel","Text","Math"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[310,4],"start":[297,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","GPU","Kernel","Text","Predicates"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[317,4],"start":[312,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","GPU","Kernel","Text","Presets"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[172,4],"start":[81,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","GPU","Kernel","Text","Types"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[212,4],"start":[174,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","GPU","Kernel","Text","Vector"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSp